#: ../../../dev/howto-docs.rst:255
msgid "Common Doxygen Tags:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../dev/howto-docs.rst:258
msgid ""
"For more tags/commands, please take a look at https://www.doxygen.nl/manual/"
"commands.html"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../dev/howto-docs.rst:260
msgid "``@brief``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../dev/howto-docs.rst:262
msgid ""
"Starts a paragraph that serves as a brief description. By default the first "
"sentence of the documentation block is automatically treated as a brief "
"description, since option `JAVADOC_AUTOBRIEF <https://www.doxygen.nl/manual/"
"config.html#cfg_javadoc_autobrief>`__ is enabled within doxygen "
"configurations."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../dev/howto-docs.rst:267
msgid "``@details``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../dev/howto-docs.rst:269
msgid ""
"Just like ``@brief`` starts a brief description, ``@details`` starts the "
"detailed description. You can also start a new paragraph (blank line) then "
"the ``@details`` command is not needed."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../dev/howto-docs.rst:272
msgid "``@param``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../dev/howto-docs.rst:274
msgid ""
"Starts a parameter description for a function parameter with name <parameter-"
"name>, followed by a description of the parameter. The existence of the "
"parameter is checked and a warning is given if the documentation of this (or "
"any other) parameter is missing or not present in the function declaration "
"or definition."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../dev/howto-docs.rst:279
msgid "``@return``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../dev/howto-docs.rst:281
msgid ""
"Starts a return value description for a function. Multiple adjacent "
"``@return`` commands will be joined into a single paragraph. The ``@return`` "
"description ends when a blank line or some other sectioning command is "
"encountered."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../dev/howto-docs.rst:285
msgid "``@code/@endcode``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../dev/howto-docs.rst:287
msgid ""
"Starts/Ends a block of code. A code block is treated differently from "
"ordinary text. It is interpreted as source code."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../dev/howto-docs.rst:290
msgid "``@rst/@endrst``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../dev/howto-docs.rst:292
msgid "Starts/Ends a block of reST markup."
msgstr ""

